<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL20">
<l>pāyunī raraṅkan taṉṉuṭ pāmpaṇaip paḷḷi koṇṭa</l>
<l>māyaṉār tiruṉaṉ mārpum marakata vuruvun tōḷum</l>
<l>tūyatā maraikkaṇ kaḷun tuvaritaḻp pavaḷa vāyu</l>
<l>māyacīr muṭiyun tēcu maṭiyarōrk kakala lāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Can the servants part from</l>
<l rend="indent">the sacred chest with Śrī,</l>
<l rend="indent">the hue of the emerald,</l>
<l rend="indent">the shoulders,</l>
<l rend="indent">the pure lotus eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">the coral mouth with scarlet lips,</l>
<l rend="indent">the excellent crown,</l>
<l rend="indent">the lustre</l>
<l>of the Dark One who sleeps on the serpent bed</l>
<l>inside Raṅgam where the water flows?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
